    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts pressure head within 8% and relative hemolysis index within 15% of experimental data across the CPB operating envelope. RH < 1.0 criterion confirmed for all worst-case operating conditions. The model is judged credible for the COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
